## Implementation order

Phase 0 → parser → types → **contracts + Lean (2e–2f) before fast codegen ships** → MIR/LLVM/OpenMP → proved Tetris + parallel benchmarks → self-host.

Do not land syntax or perf features that bypass the Lean gate.
